The @costumeindustrycoalition is honored to partner with the @sixthemusical and @sixbroadway to host a “SIX” Zoom Party! ✨💜👑 This Zoom Party will be a conversation with the #SIX Costume Creative team: Costume Designer Gabriella Slade @sladegabriella NYC Costume Shop Owner John Kristiansen @jpkny.inc and Costume Associate Lisa Zinni @lisazinni as they discuss the “SIX” queens’ design inspiration, design sketches, construction process. Hosted by our CIC Associate @edwinschiff 

But we don’t want them to have all the fun, we want to include you, (yes you!), to be part of the party! ✨Ever wonder what inspired @sladegabriella design? Or how in the world @jpkny.inc got those skirt’s just right? Well, now is your chance to ask those questions and show off your own costumes, artwork and interpretations of ​#SIXCostumes 💜

Send your 30 second video questions to sixzoomparty@gmail.com by September 7th and six lucky winners will be selected to win the CROWN PRIZE 👑 of your question aired during the “SIX” Zoom Party and answered by the panel. One lucky winner will be selected for the GRAND PRIZE ✨and will receive a signed sketch from @sladegabriella 

We can’t wait to join the #Queendom 👑 of this incredible show. Join us on September 16th at 12:00pm EST for this #SIXZoomParty 
.
